caption.body: The New York #Giants face off against the Miami #Dolphins in tonight’s #MondayNightFootball game. In 1972, the Miami Dolphins posted the NFL's only perfect season with a 17-0 record, which was topped by a 14-7 victory over the Washington Redskins in Super Bowl VII. New York Giants fans are among the most passionate in the league, and the team currently has more than 135,000 fans waitlisted for season tickets. Which team are you rooting for?  Check out your favorite NFL team’s case, in our exhibition "The Nation's Game", post-security, in Terminal 3!
